title: Results-focused training
content: ['Certified Fitness Coaches Our certified personal trainers are inducted and trained by in-house programs globally recognised by American Council on Exercise (ACE), National Academy of Sports Medicine (NASM), Fitness Edutraining Asia (FEA).', 'QUALIFIED AND CERTIFIED All our Certified Fitness Coaches are required to complete a vigorous foundation training program spanning 3 to 12 months. Our coaches are required to pass all exams before being allowed to train our clients.', 'OUR COACHES PRACTICE THE 5 KEY PILLARS OF FITNESS', 'POSTURE Correcting your posture will reduce stress and strain on your body. You’ll stand taller, move better, and feel less fatigue. MOBILITY Good mobility allows your body to move the way it was designed to move – pain free and with a good range of motion. CORE Your core is part of almost every move you make. Strong core muscles act as a stabilizer, making moving safer and more efficient. STRENGTH Strength training helps you develop strong bones, manage weight and help you do everyday activities better and easier. CARDIO Improving your cardio will strengthen your stamina and endurance so you can work harder for long and burn more calories.', 'Ignite your fitness journey', '01 READY Our coaches begin with posture and movement assessment, utilising the latest tools - Boditrax and MyCoach, to track your progress and identify areas to improve.', '02 SET Expert coaches teach pre-workout stretching and muscle activation, post-workout cool-down techniques, and foam roller use to relieve muscle soreness.', '03 GO Dynamic Movement Training emphasizes utilizing natural movements to enhance core strength and improve cardio. Coaches will guide you through the process.']
